<p>I need to check entity in geenric service if it is Entity type, I should add dynamic expression where <code>.Where("IsDeleted==false");</code></p>  <pre><code>var result = _entityRepo.All();  var isEntityType = typeof(Entity).IsAssignableFrom(typeof(T)); if (isEntityType) {     var expression = CreateExpression("IsDeleted", true);     var casted = (Expression&lt;Func&lt;T, bool&gt;&gt;)expression;     result = result.Where(casted); } return result; </code></pre>  <p><code>_entityRepo</code> is <code>GenericRepository&lt;T&gt;</code></p>  <pre><code>public static Expression CreateExpression(string propertyName, bool valueToCompare) {     // get the type of entity     var entityType = typeof(Entity);     // get the type of the value object     var entityProperty = entityType.GetProperty(propertyName);      // Expression: "entity"     var parameter = Expression.Parameter(entityType, "entity");      // check if the property type is a value type     // only value types work     // Expression: entity.Property == value     return Expression.Equal(         Expression.Property(parameter, entityProperty),         Expression.Constant(valueToCompare)     ); } </code></pre>  <p>off course I get error on cast:</p>  <blockquote>   <p>Unable to cast object of type   'System.Linq.Expressions.LogicalBinaryExpression' to type   'System.Linq.Expressions.Expression<code>1[System.Func</code>2[MadCloud.Domain.Auditing.AuditCategory,System.Boolean]]'.</p> </blockquote>